                     <interp inst="t18470510-1246-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18470510-1246-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp> for stealing 1 purse, value 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>., and 1 groat; the property of <persName id="t18470510-name-805" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18470510-name-805" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
